---

<Layout
  title='About'
  description='Learn about my journey as a full-stack web developer, from computer science education to creating modern web applications. Passionate about building innovative digital solutions and user-focused experiences.'
>
  <section class='container space-y-6'>
    <Breadcrumb />

    <div class='space-y-8 text-lg leading-relaxed'>
      <div class='space-y-6'>
        <h1 class='text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight lg:text-5xl'>About</h1>
        <p>
          Born in 1996, I grew up alongside the digital revolution, witnessing the internet evolve into the powerful
          platform it is today. My journey into web development started with pure curiosity - I wanted to understand how
          websites worked and soon found myself <span class='highlight'>building my own digital experiences</span>.
        </p>

        <p>
          After completing my <span class='highlight'>Computer Science degree at Singidunum University</span>, I've
          dedicated myself to mastering modern web development and creating solutions that make a difference. From
          browser extensions to full-stack applications, I approach each project as an opportunity to innovate and grow.
        </p>

        <p>
          Today, I specialize in building <span class='highlight'>modern web applications</span> that prioritize performance,
          accessibility, and user experience. I'm particularly passionate about exploring new technologies and finding creative
          ways to solve complex problems through code.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class='space-y-6'>
        <h2 class='text-2xl font-bold'>Tech I Love Working With</h2>
        <div class='grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 sm:grid-cols-3 md:grid-cols-6'>
          {
            techStack.map((tech) => (
              <div
                class={cn(
                  'bg-base-200 hover:bg-base-300 flex flex-col items-center gap-2 rounded-lg p-4 transition-all duration-300',
                  'hover:shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(0,0,0,0.1)]',
                  tech.hover,
                )}
              >
                <Icon name={tech.icon} class={`size-8 ${tech.color} opacity-85`} />
                <span class={'text-base-content text-sm font-medium'}>{tech.name}</span>
              </div>
            ))
          }
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class='space-y-6'>
        <h2 class='text-2xl font-bold'>Fun Facts</h2>
        <div class='grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2'>
          {
            funFacts.map((fact) => (
              <div
                class={cn(
                  'bg-base-200 group flex items-center gap-4 rounded-lg p-4',
                  'hover:bg-base-300/50 hover:-translate-y-0.5',
                  'transition-all duration-300 ease-out',
                  'hover:shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(0,0,0,0.1)]',
                  fact.glow,
                )}
              >
                <div class='relative'>
                  <Icon
                    name={fact.icon}
                    class={cn('size-5 shrink-0', 'transition-all duration-300', fact.color, 'group-hover:scale-110')}
                  />
                  <div
                    class={cn(
                      'absolute inset-0 -z-10 opacity-0 blur',
                      'transition-opacity duration-300 ease-out',
                      'group-hover:opacity-50',
                      fact.color.replace('group-hover:', ''),
                    )}
                  />
                </div>
                <span class='group-hover:text-base-content/90 transition-colors duration-300'>{fact.text}</span>
              </div>
            ))
          }
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class='from-secondary/20 to-warning/20 space-y-4 rounded-lg bg-gradient-to-r p-6 text-lg'>
        <p>
          I'm always open to discussing new projects, opportunities, or just having a chat about web development. Feel
          free to check out my <a href='/projects' class='text-secondary font-medium underline'>projects</a> or connect with
          me on <a
            href='https://github.com/aleksa-codes'
            target='_blank'
            rel='noopener noreferrer'
            class='text-secondary font-medium underline'
          >
            GitHub
          </a>.
        </p>
        <div class='flex items-center gap-2'>
          <Button href='mailto:hello@aleksa.codes' variant='ghost' size='sm'>
            <Icon name='lucide:mail' />
            Email me
          </Button>
          <Button
            href='https://discordapp.com/users/1078249969775038514'
            variant='ghost'
            size='sm'
            target='_blank'
            rel='noopener noreferrer'
          >
            <Icon name='simple-icons:discord' />
            Discord
          </Button>
        </div>
        <p class='font-cursive text-right text-3xl font-bold select-none sm:text-4xl'>aleksa</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
